rawing on a range of genres and firsthand encounters, he reveals that our fascination with Nordic societies and our love for Nordic music might be more intertwined than first thought.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2022) 0aMusicxSocial aspectszScandinavia. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Classical.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300265491?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300265491423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300265491/original  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles